OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FLush to stop some social   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmedia until it's 'safer'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Cosmetics firm Lush says it is         
OL,6, deactivating some social media accounts
OL,7, until platforms "take action to provide
OL,8, a safer environment" for users.        
OL,10,FThe company said that from Friday, its 
OL,11,FInstagram, Facebook, TikTok and        
OL,12,FSnapchat pages will be shut down.      
OL,14,FThe policy will be rolled out across   
OL,15,Fall 48 countries Lush operates in.     
OL,17,FHowever, the company will continue to  
OL,18,Foperate on Twitter and YouTube "for    
OL,19,Fnow", as looks to "build better        
OL,20,Fchannels of communication elsewhere".  
